ge" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift-Photo-by-Emma-McIntyre_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift-Photo-by-Emma-McIntyre_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift-Photo-by-Emma-McIntyre_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift-Photo-by-Emma-McIntyre_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift-Photo-by-Emma-McIntyre_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift-Photo-by-Emma-McIntyre_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>新数据显示，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的</a><i>《时代》一</i>书在发售首周末就售出超过 80 万册。</p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454"><b>泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）——《受折磨的诗人部》评论：罕见的失误</b></a></li></ul><p>根据 Circana（来自<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/music-news/taylor-swift-eras-book-sales-first-weekend-1236078174/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《好莱坞报道</i></a>》）的数据，该书在美国感恩节假期周末售出 814,000 册。</p><p>该书在美国仅通过 Target 销售，尚未通过亚马逊等渠道购买。</p><p>斯威夫特最近在社交媒体上发布了这本书的消息，该书与 12 月 8 日最后一场“ <a href="https://news.sky.com/story/taylor-swift-v-the-beatles-as-the-eras-tour-hits-the-uk-how-does-the-star-compare-against-the-biggest-band-of-all-time-13142432">Eras”巡演</a>同一天发​​行。</p><p>这一销量使斯威夫特与巴拉克·奥巴马(Barack Obama)处于类似的地位，后者的总统回忆录<i>《应许之地</i>》在 2020 年上架第一周就售出了 816,000 册。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/